Topics in Algorithms </h3>
<h3 style="font-family: Comic Sans MS; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The
topic
for Spring 2010 is Science of Power Management<br>
</h3>
<h3 style="font-family: Comic Sans MS; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</h3>
<h3 style="font-family: Comic Sans MS; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Instructor</h3>
