      <td style="vertical-align: top; font-family: Comic Sans MS;">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="http://www.cs.pitt.edu/cast/papers/cho-micro09.pdf">Flip-N-Write:
A
Simple
Deterministic
Technique
to
Improve
PRAM
Write
Performance,
