and
Endurance</a> by Sangyeun Cho and Hyunjin Lee, MICRO 2009. (<a
 href="flip-n-write_slides.pdf">Slides</a>)<br>
        </li>
        <li>A Content-Aware Block Placement Algorithm for Reducing PRAM
Storage Bit Writes<br>
by Brian Wongchaowart, Marian K. Iskander, and Sangyeun Cho (<a
 href="block_placement_slides.pdf">Slides</a>)<br>
        </li>
      </ul>
      </td>
